reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Cute bag - love the flat lay
reviews.reviewText: I got these for a favorite things party because I have been using a similar makeup bag for a long time and love it. Pros - tons of storage and lays flat when open for easy access. Can put small palettes blush etc in the side pockets and brushes in the middle pocket. Con - the material of this one is super thin and flimsy. That said, it still works great for makeup but I’m not sure how well the construction will hold over time so one star off for that and flimsy material. It was well received at the party with the super cute colors and lettering.
